metadata.name: Astral Graffiti
metadata.created_by: Susanna Rosso Wolf (SR Wolf Studio Arts)
metadata.description: Astral Graffiti is a 30x40” acrylic, oil and ink painting on stretched cotton canvas. This painting is the first of her astral collection and was inspired by her fascination with space, the astral world and what she herself could be doing up there in her afterlife. Wolf visualizes the astral realm as she contemplates her compositions of space, in space and time.
